<section id="FAQs">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 current" id="faqid">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 faq" id="myqid">
        <h2>My Queries</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 current" id="laqid">
        <h2>Latest Queries</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row myqueries" id="faqdiv">
      <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
          <li><a data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#math1" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="math1 cp">How can I reach NSUT?</a></li>
          <ul class="collapse list-unstyled" id = "math1">
            <li>The best way to reach NSUT is by metro. The college is only 01 Km from Dwarka Mor Metro Station.</li>
          </ul>
          <li><a data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#cp" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="cp">How do I apply for a hostel at NSUT?</a></li>
          <ul class="collapse list-unstyled" id = "cp">
            <li>You will need Self-attested copy of Confirmation of Provisional Admission in B. E. program at NSUT, Self-attested copy of NSUT Admission Fee Slip, and 5 Color Photos (Two Stamp size and Three passport size).</li>
          </ul>
          <li><a data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#ene" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="ene"> Is there WIFI in NSUT hostels?</a></li>
          <ul class="collapse list-unstyled" id = "ene">
            <li>Yes, high speed Wfi is available 24 hours.</li>
          </ul>
          <li><a data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#phy" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="phy">How many hostels are there in NSIT?</a></li>
          <ul class="collapse list-unstyled" id = "phy">
            <li>NSUT currently has 4 hostels.</li>
          </ul>
          <li><a data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#eng" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="eng">Which is better IIIT or NSUT?</a></li>
          <ul class="collapse list-unstyled" id = "eng">
            <li>For research, innovation, and higher studies, IIIT Delhi is a better choice but if you are interested in placement, infrastructure, and college life, NSUT is far better than any other college</li>
          </ul>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
          <li><a data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#math3" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="math3 cp1">Which all languages should I start learning first?</a></li>
          <ul class="collapse list-unstyled" id = "math3">
            <li>Start with C and Python and then move on to C++.</li>
          </ul>
          <li><a data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#cp1" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="cp1">Which all are the tech societies in NSUT?</a></li>
          <ul class="collapse list-unstyled" id = "cp1">
            <li>IOSD and GDSC</li>
          </ul>
          <li><a data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#ene1" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="ene1">What percentage of attendance should I maintain?</a></li>
          <ul class="collapse list-unstyled" id = "ene1">
            <li>At least 80%</li>
          </ul>
          <li><a data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#phy1" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="phy1">How should I prepare for the mid semester exams?</a></li>
          <ul class="collapse list-unstyled" id = "phy1">
            <li>Just pay 100% attention in class since most of the questions are already discusses in the class.</li>
          </ul>
          <li><a data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#eng1" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="eng1">I am in COE. I wasnâ€™t able to get CSAI. Does it matter?</a></li>
          <ul class="collapse list-unstyled" id = "eng1">
            <li>No. Both are equally good branches with almost the same syllabus</li>
          </ul>
          
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row" id="myqdiv">

  <% if(login === "Sign in"){ %>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary sign-in"><a href="/login" style="color:white;">Sign-in to continue.</a></button>

  <% } else{ %>

    <div class=" proper">
      <form action="/Queries" method="post">
        <!-- Query : <input type="text" class="QueryBox" name="queryname" placeholder="Write your query here"> -->
        <textarea name="queryname" class="QueryBox" placeholder="Write your query here" cols="50" rows="3"></textarea>
        <br>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-warning ">Ask a doubt</button>
      </form>
      
    </div>
    <div class ="small-heading">
      <p>Past Queries</p>
    </div>
    
    <% if(queryList.length==0){ %>
      <div class=" card proper" id="normal">
      <h2>No Queries Asked Yet.</h2>
    </div>
    <% }else{ %>
      <!-- document.getElementById('normal').classList.remove('proper'); -->
      <div class="card proper" style="height: auto;" id="normal">
      <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="accordionFlushExample">
        <% for(let i=queryList.length-1;i>=0;i--){ %>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-heading<%= i%>">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapse<%= i%>" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapse<%= i%>">
                <%= queryList[i].query %>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="flush-collapse<%= i%>" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-heading<%= i%>" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
              <% if(queryList[i].answers.length==0){ %>
                <div class="accordion-body">No one answered yet.</div>
              <% }else{ %>
                <% for(let j=queryList[i].answers.length-1;j>=0;j--){ %>
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    <%= queryList[i].answers[j].answer %>
                    <p style="color: black;">- by <%= queryList[i].answers[j].user %></p>
                  </div>
                <% } %>
              <% } %>
              <div class="addAnswer">
                <form action="/Answer" method="post">
                  <textarea class="answertext" placeholder="Type your answer here..." rows="1" name="answerArea"></textarea>
                  <input type="" value="<%= queryList[i].id %>" name="queryId" style="display: none;">
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-dark postAnswer">Post</button>
                </form>
              </div>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      </div>
    <% } %>
    <%  } %>
  </div>

  
  <div class="row myqueries" id="laqdiv">
    <% if(login === "Sign in"){ %>
      <div class=" card proper">
        <h2>Sign-in to see all Queries.</h2>
        </div>
  
    <% } else{ %>
    <% if(queryLatestList.length==0){ %>
      <div class=" card proper">
      <h2>No Queries asked yet.</h2>
      </div>
    <% }else{ %>
      <div class="card proper" style="height: auto;">
      <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="accordionFlushExample1">
        <% for(let i=queryLatestList.length-1;i>=0;i--){ %>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-heading<%= i%>">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapse<%= i%>" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapse<%= i%>">
                <%= queryLatestList[i].query %>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="flush-collapse<%= i%>" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-heading<%= i%>" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample1">
              <% if(queryLatestList[i].answers.length==0){ %>
                <div class="accordion-body">No one answered yet.</div>
              <% }else{ %>
                <% for(let j=queryLatestList[i].answers.length-1;j>=0;j--){ %>
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    <%= queryLatestList[i].answers[j].answer %>
                    <p style="color: black;">- by <%= queryLatestList[i].answers[j].user %></p>
                  </div>
                <% } %>
              <% } %>
              <div class="addAnswer">
                <form action="/Answer" method="post">
                  <textarea class="answertext" placeholder="Type your answer here..." rows="1" name="answerArea"></textarea>
                  <input type="" value="<%= queryLatestList[i].id %>" name="queryId" style="display: none;">
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-dark postAnswer">Post</button>
                </form>
              </div>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      </div>
    <% } %>
    <% } %>
  </div>
